%% Diagram: QUIC connection migration via Connection IDs
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server

    Note over C,S: WiFi 4-tuple
    C->>S: 1-RTT packets DCID=CID_S
    S->>C: 1-RTT packets DCID=CID_C

    Note over C: Hand-off to cellular (NAT rebinding)
    C->>S: Probe from new 4-tuple DCID=CID_S
    S->>C: PATH_CHALLENGE (8 random bytes)
    C->>S: PATH_RESPONSE (echoes same 8 bytes)
    Note over C,S: New path validated. Same CID. No re-handshake.

    C->>S: 1-RTT packets from cellular 4-tuple
